unless you signed a Pre-Nup,

31:07.098 --> 31:09.566
there's really no getting around
the... uh, community property

31:09.567 --> 31:10.401
laws in this state.

31:10.402 --> 31:12.135
Community property!

31:12.136 --> 31:15.539
