33:05.149 --> 33:08.518
Uh... that's too bad.

33:08.519 --> 33:12.322
The handwriting was on the wall
if you ask me. Old Heather

33:12.323 --> 33:15.759
had all sorts of problems,
mental and otherwise.

33:15.760 --> 33:17.361
Including trying to sleep
with every guy...

33:17.362 --> 33:19.296
Wait, wait a minute. Did...
did you say her name was...

33:19.297 --> 33:23.368
Yeah, good old pill
popping Heather.

33:23.534 --> 33:26.270
That lady was the biggest whore
in the county.

33:26.804 --> 33:29.840
I tried to warn Bobby before he
got married to that bitch.

33:29.841 --> 33:32.642
Wouldn t ya know he didn t
talk to me for almost a year

33:32.643 --> 33:34.111
after that.

33:34.112 --> 33:38.782
Well, they found her around noon
sprawled out on the bathroom

33:38.783 --> 33:41.419
floor in some motel up the
highway.

33:41.686 --> 33:43.153
Mo... motel?

33:43.154 --> 33:47.124
